alwaysApply: true
---

Path: `salons/{salonId}/sales/{saleId}` — models: `lib/features/sales/data/models/sale.dart` (`Sale`, `SaleLineItem`).

## Document fields

id: string
salonId: string
employeeId: string
barberId: string (mirrors employeeId when unset; for queries/reporting)
employeeName: string

lineItems: array of maps (each line item):
  serviceId: string
  serviceName: string
  employeeId: string
  employeeName: string
  quantity: number
  unitPrice: number
  total: number

serviceNames: array of string (denormalized, all service names on the sale)

subtotal: number
tax: number
discount: number
total: number

paymentMethod: string — `SalePaymentMethods`: cash | card | digital_wallet | other
status: string — `SaleStatuses`: completed | pending | refunded | voided

soldAt: timestamp
customerId: string (nullable — `users/{uid}`)
customerName: string (optional)
reportYear: number
reportMonth: number
reportPeriodKey: string (YYYY-MM)
createdByUid: string (optional)
createdByName: string (optional)
createdAt: timestamp
updatedAt: timestamp

## Implemented vs Planned

**Implemented:** Full POS-style sale with `lineItems` and totals; constants in `lib/core/constants/sale_reporting.dart`.

**Planned:** None required for current MVP; extend enums if you add payment providers.
